data.name: UpdateElectronicFundTransmission
data.value: update CKT_ELEC_FUND_TRAN set LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, TRANS_STATUS_CODE = @transStatusCode, TRANS_PROCESS_DATE = @transProcessDate where (TRANSMISSION_TYPE = @transmissionType) and (TRANSMISSION_ID = @transmissionId)
